Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸計劃 進入第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A.G.140年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「驅蝠戰役」後25年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦與火星圈國家維甘的戰爭仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對維甘日漸擴大的勢力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正緊鑼密鼓地準備著大規模反擊戰役
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼？ 艾倫格雷亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ader的試運行實驗前些天完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性能出色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它立即服役的呼聲非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ader是在高達AGE-1的基礎上設計完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先配備給前線部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是在構思作戰計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼滴水不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找出維甘的所有藏身地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們趕出這個宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭 還會持續多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說戰爭的開端 「天使隕落」事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰巧是司令出生的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府多次提出過議和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們卻一概拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒有正常人的邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與他們談和是對牛彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令還是認為 必須將維甘徹底剿滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是全人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令擁有靈活的判斷力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨在這一點上卻毫不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說這始終是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我的想法錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是斯萊斯雷茲軍校首席畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼應該明白作為參謀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須積極理解司令官的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點不用我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 這次休假是和家人團聚？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…不知道他現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你們是什麼機動戰士社團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天在校舍後面吱吱卡卡的煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我們是經過學校同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是找碴來要錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多餘的零花錢不如拿出來大家分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有舊式人工智能芯片級的智商
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想來要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子不想活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為所有人都怕你們就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個亞瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仗著自己是聯邦軍司令的兒子 囂張是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你知道什麼叫後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師如果沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆早把他們打得四腳朝天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 學校裏打架沒好果子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 他們可能還會來報復
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再扁一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動了動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威！馬希爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大概是手腕的驅動控制系統還有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啊大哥 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 剛才的聲音好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗·斯通主動和我們說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能造出這樣的東西太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機…機動戰士方面是我們的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗 小心弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一股機油味 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗還是那麼可愛 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被機動戰士纏身的家族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你還記著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 尤諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真難得 爸爸能趕回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 上次是什麼時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特現在是聯邦軍的司令官了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能總是放下軍務陪著家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 17歲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 麻煩再來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 吃得太多可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 外公太貪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤諾亞怎麼也說我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第三盤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是明日野家族世代相傳的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家族世代相傳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆遲早必須繼承它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久自然會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會保護你 和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕 便宜都給哥哥佔了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時時刻刻都要帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會保管好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論發生什麼 你也要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是明日野家族繼承者的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 下周有機動戰士大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他們在為衛冕做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 假期只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就必須出門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給斯萊斯雷茲軍校寫推薦信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精英學校不好讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要用功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 想讓我當軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班級又有了新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是傑哈特·葛雷德同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座學校裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以走在走廊正中間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是那個轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是洛德阿布斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教會你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 初來乍到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 明白了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部分和其他關鍵驅動沒有形成聯動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把轉力控制程序換成先前的版本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏要換的話 其他關節也得換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備份在哪裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的版本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那版本也有問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有興趣加入機動戰士社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看條件差 去年還得了托爾迪亞冠軍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已掌握進入衛星的路徑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕的動作還是沒有改進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要求太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重寫關節驅動程序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周後就比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想輸給德魯斯緹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都想贏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你這是在急什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得冠軍 被老爸的認可是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得已經很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…不是因為那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在格鬥大賽上奪冠 沒什麼錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急避難警報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽明明說托爾迪亞戒備森嚴不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是居民區的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去大家都會遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 媽媽的電話也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把腳扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去 我和家裏人聯繫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆　這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 尤諾亞她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 和艾米莉一起到地下避難…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她受傷了 不能丟下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬瑟 漢斯 咋樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是菲利特製造出的最強機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的機動戰士竟然在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 菲利特那小子故意藏在這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護這座衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它去…作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸知道會有這麼一天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 到關鍵時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須承擔起保護大家的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是明日野家族的男人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會保護你和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會和爸爸那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 我決定干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能動？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常維護從沒有怠慢過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的性能遠遠勝過菲利特當年用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 開動它的話馬廄不會塌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別操心 喬瑟！漢斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE裝置就是鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE裝置…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來它就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心著點 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士的基本操作我全掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主監視器點亮 能量系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來！ 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞瑟姆在駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行 我能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幹掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有上 我必須保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 看我一定幹掉你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 二刀流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 鎮靜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個機師讓人感覺稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩一台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了 贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台Dorado 就這麼完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高達的性能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這霧是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達從視野中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於還是開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓你品嚐到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去寶貴的人的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆　高達就托付給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:24:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士大賽當天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的影子潛伏在高達身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情與戀情與機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰凍睡眠是 讓人類以睡眠的狀態冰凍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對肉體進行長期保存的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飛船乘員使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以節約航行過程中的食物和氧氣消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持年輕的身體前往遙遠的未來

